  "original_title": "\u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dca.\u0d86\u0dbb\u0dca. \u0d9a\u0dda\u0dad\u0dba \u0dc3\u0db8\u0d9c \u0dc0\u0dcf\u0dc4\u0db1\u0dba\u0dda \u0d85\u0d82\u0d9a\u0dba\u0da7 \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0db4\u0dd9\u0da7\u0dca\u0d9a\u0ddd \u0d89\u0db1\u0dca\u0db0\u0db1 \u0dbd\u0db6\u0db1 21\u0daf\u0dcf \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Q.R. From 21st receive Cipetco fuel to vehicle number with code",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The President of the Petrol Station Owners Association said today (18th) that according to the fuel license, the fuel will be released next Thursday (21st) and until then there will be no problem in queuing at Sipetco filling stations.",
        "From Thursday, Q.R. The chairman also mentioned that fuel will be issued only according to the code and the registration number of the vehicle and accordingly only the vehicle owners whose last digit of the vehicle registration number is 0, 1 and 2 should come to get fuel on the 21st."
      ],
